Package: theme.aagi
Version: 0.0.1
Title: Apply AAGI Brand Guidelines to Graphic Output and Create AAGI Themed Documents
Description: Applies 'AAGI' external brand guidelines to graphics. 'AAGI'
    colours and font guidelines are applied as useful and reasonable to both
    base graphics as well as 'ggplot2' figures.  Support for creating MS Word
    and PowerPoint files using Quarto and RMarkdown templates is also provided.
